 *Benchmark for Western Massively Multiplayer Online Games* 
 *BELLEVUE Wash. – 16th...</description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div><a href="http://www.guildwars2hub.com/news/guild-wars-2-fastest-selling-mmo-history" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">http://www.guildwars2hub.com/news/gu...ng-mmo-history</a><br />
